node.text: On this 188th episode of the #Bisimoto #Tech2sday show, we talk about engine and exhaust coatings, car myths, infusing classic cars with modern tech, should I grow my hair, the new #AcuraIntegra and more. Enjoy!

node.text: Today, we discussed the EPA and CARB car mandates, #MotorMythbusters, safe mods to make power, COVID in the UK, my thoughts on performance EVs, and more. Episode 182 of the #Bisimoto #Tech2sday show.

node.text: On this 188th episode of the #Bisimoto #Tech2sday show, we talk about engine and exhaust coatings, car myths, infusing classic cars with modern tech, should I grow my hair, the new #AcuraIntegra and more. Enjoy!

Congratulations to @PorscheOntario for winning the western region award for the #PorscheRestorationChallenge21.
This is such a huge honour, and I am proud of the team.
See you at the nationals in Indy!
